yc = 49.0
ys = 0.05
ty = 0.001
zc = 51.0
zs = 0.04
tz = -0.002
dist = 112.345
not_trans = transform.compute_tth_eta(self.peaks, y_center=yc, y_size=ys,
    tilt_y=ty, z_center=zc, z_size=zs, tilt_z=tz, distance=dist)
om = np.ones(self.peaks.shape[1], np.float)
trans = transform.compute_tth_eta(self.peaks, y_center=yc, y_size=ys,
    tilt_y=ty, z_center=zc, z_size=zs, tilt_z=tz, distance=dist, t_x=0.0,
    t_y=0.0, t_z=0.0, omega=om, wedge=10.0, chi=-11.0)
diff = not_trans[0] - trans[0]
self.assertAlmostEqual(np.sum(diff * diff), 0, 5)
diff = not_trans[1] - trans[1]
self.assertAlmostEqual(np.sum(diff * diff), 0, 5)
